projects.name: FriendPost
projects.description: Socialize and share thoughts. Built with React, GraphQL, Apollo, MongoDB, NodeJS, and Semantic UI.

projects.name: ReCaller
projects.description: Schedule phone calls with others and have your conversations transcribed with DeepGram's speech recognition technology. Recordings and transcriptions are stored in your account and can be sent directly to your email.

projects.name: Mentor Me
projects.description: Mentor Me connects people with questions to people with answers. I built the back end for this application with NodeJs and Express. Users can create a secure account, post questions, and post answers.

projects.name: Game Of Life
projects.description: Game of Life showcases cellular automation. I built this with React and used algorithm to determine if cells die or live on to the next generation.

projects.name: I'll Serve Soup
projects.description: A landing page I made for a soup kitchen inventory app. Built with HTML, LESS, and Javascript.
